outputs.output_descr:
The main purpose of the PA can be outlined as follows: 
•	Provide the opportunity for close, continued consultation with SIG and Provincial Governments to ensure full local ownership of the upcoming five year PGSP joint program;
•	Undertake the analytical work needed to inform the formulation of the PGSP, to prepare the joint program document, and to ensure a rapid start up of PGSP;
•	Provide human resource support to bring essential staffing levels in the MPGIS and the provinces up to minimum levels required for the implementation of training and other PGSP activities; and
•	Address basic logistics requirements (communications, minor office repairs) of the MPGIS and Provincial Governments to improve the working environment and enable them to effectively participate in the PGSP.
